# 4. 가장 많이 주문한 사람의 아이디와 이름, 주문개수는? ???
SELECT * FROM t_order;
SELECT * FROM t_user;
SELECT * FROM t_product;

SELECT userNo FROM t_order; #이걸 세자
SELECT userNo, COUNT(userNo) FROM t_order; 
SELECT userNo, COUNT(userNo) FROM t_order GROUP BY userNo; 
SELECT userNo, COUNT(userNo) FROM t_order GROUP BY userNo ORDER BY COUNT(userNo); 
SELECT userNo, COUNT(userNo) FROM t_order GROUP BY userNo ORDER BY COUNT(userNo) DESC LIMIT 1; 
SELECT userId, userName FROM t_user WHERE id = 1;

SELECT *#####################################
FROM t_order INNER JOIN t_user ON t_order.userNo = t_user.id
INNER JOIN t_product ON t_order.productNo = t_product.id
GROUP BY t_user.id
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1;

	SELECT t_user.userId,t_user.userName, COUNT(t_order.id) AS '주문개수'
	FROM t_user JOIN t_order ON t_user.id = t_order.userNo
	GROUP BY t_user.id, t_user.userId, t_user.userName
	ORDER BY '주문개수' 
	DESC LIMIT 1;

